  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe ? \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9 ?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Need to wear a face mask again? What is the recommendation of the Ministry of Health?",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "In view of the Covid-19 situation in the country, the Ministry of Health has strongly advised the public to wear face masks.",
        "The Ministry of Health has made this recommendation on the advice of the Director General of Health Services, Dr. Asela Gunawardena.",
        "According to this, the Ministry of Health has requested the public to wear face covering while in indoor places, public gatherings and traveling using public transport services.",
        "The number of Covid-19 infections in Sri Lanka is on the rise again after several months, according to statistics from the Ministry of Health's Epidemiology Division.",
        "Meanwhile, while more than 500 Covid infected people have been identified in the country in the last 10 days, it is noteworthy that 75 new Covid infected people have been identified only on Monday, the 25th of yesterday.",
        "In view of the current spread of Covid-19 in the country, the Ministry of Health has strongly recommended wearing face masks again."
      ],
